    <description><![CDATA[<h2 id="下载" class="headerLink">
    <a href="#%e4%b8%8b%e8%bd%bd" class="header-mark"></a>下载</h2><ul>
<li><a href="https://portswigger.net/burp/releases#professional" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">BurpSuite</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/Leon406/BurpSuiteCN-Release/releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">注册启动汉化</a></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="安装" class="headerLink">
    <a href="#%e5%ae%89%e8%a3%85" class="header-mark"></a>安装</h2><ol>
<li>安装完成后先启动一次burp，然后关闭，否则会报错损坏。</li>
<li>在应用程序中找到BurpSuite右键显示包内容，依次打开 ./Contents/Resources/app，把启动器放入其中。</li>
<li>返回到Contents目录，编辑vmoptions.txt，末尾追加内容</li>
</ol>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span><span class="lnt">3
</span><span class="lnt">4
</span><span class="lnt">5
</span><span class="lnt">6
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-txt" data-lang="txt"><span class="line"><span class="cl">--add-opens=java.base/java.lang=ALL-UNNAMED
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">--add-opens=java.base/jdk.internal.org.objectweb.asm=ALL-UNNAMED
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">--add-opens=java.base/jdk.internal.org.objectweb.asm.tree=ALL-UNNAMED
